net.dragondelve.customdriversutil.model.generator

Class GridGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dragondelve.customdriversutil.model.generator.GridGenerator

  • public class GridGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Grid Generator. Generates a new grid when the generateNewGrid() method is called. The grid is generated based on GeneratorSettings and the ValueGenerator provided. If no value generator is provided in the constructor it will generate a grid with empty values.
